<section class="faq-section reveal-on-scroll" aria-labelledby="faq-title">
  <header class="faq__header">
    <h2 id="faq-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
  </header>

  <p id="faq-copy-status" class="visually-hidden" role="status" aria-live="polite"></p>

  <div class="faq__list" role="list">
    <details class="faq__item" role="listitem" id="faq-cost" open>
      <summary class="faq__question">
        <span>How much does mobile grooming cost in {{ cityName ?? '[City]' }}?</span>
        <a class="faq__anchor" href="#faq-cost" aria-label="Link to this question" title="Copy link" data-faq-anchor>
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
            <path d="M10 14l-2 2a4 4 0 1 1-5.657-5.657l3-3A4 4 0 0 1 10 9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            <path d="M14 10l2-2a4 4 0 1 1 5.657 5.657l-3 3A4 4 0 0 1 14 15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <span class="faq__chevron" aria-hidden="true">▾</span>
      </summary>
      <div class="faq__answer">
        <p>Prices vary based on your pet's size, breed, and coat condition. Filling out the form gets you a precise, no-obligation quote from a local pro.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq__item" role="listitem" id="faq-services">
      <summary class="faq__question">
        <span>What services are included?</span>
        <a class="faq__anchor" href="#faq-services" aria-label="Link to this question" title="Copy link" data-faq-anchor>
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
            <path d="M10 14l-2 2a4 4 0 1 1-5.657-5.657l3-3A4 4 0 0 1 10 9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            <path d="M14 10l2-2a4 4 0 1 1 5.657 5.657l-3 3A4 4 0 0 1 14 15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <span class="faq__chevron" aria-hidden="true">▾</span>
      </summary>
      <div class="faq__answer">
        <p>A standard groom typically includes a bath, haircut, nail trim, and ear cleaning. You can discuss specific needs with your groomer.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq__item" role="listitem" id="faq-duration">
      <summary class="faq__question">
        <span>How long does an appointment take?</span>
        <a class="faq__anchor" href="#faq-duration" aria-label="Link to this question" title="Copy link" data-faq-anchor>
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
            <path d="M10 14l-2 2a4 4 0 1 1-5.657-5.657l3-3A4 4 0 0 1 10 9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            <path d="M14 10l2-2a4 4 0 1 1 5.657 5.657l-3 3A4 4 0 0 1 14 15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <span class="faq__chevron" aria-hidden="true">▾</span>
      </summary>
      <div class="faq__answer">
        <p>Usually 1–2 hours, depending on your pet. It's much faster than a traditional salon since it's one-on-one.</p>
      </div>
    </details>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="second-cta-section reveal-on-scroll" aria-labelledby="second-cta-title">
  <header class="second-cta__header">
    <h2 id="second-cta-title">Ready to Spoil Your Pet?</h2>
    <p class="second-cta__lede">Get a quick, no-obligation quote from a trusted groomer in {{ cityName ?? '[City]' }}.</p>
  </header>

  <div class="second-cta__grid">
    <div class="second-cta__benefits" aria-hidden="false">
      <ul class="second-cta__list" role="list">
        <li class="second-cta__item">
          <div class="second-cta__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
              <path d="M12 2l6 3v5c0 4.5-3 8.5-6 9.5-3-1-6-5-6-9.5V5l6-3z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
              <path d="M9 11.5l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="second-cta__text">Vetted local pros — no spam, no obligations.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="second-cta__item">
          <div class="second-cta__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
              <path d="M12 6v6l4 2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="second-cta__text">Fast responses — most quotes in under an hour.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="second-cta__item">
          <div class="second-cta__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
              <path d="M3 6h18M3 12h18M3 18h18" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="second-cta__text">Simple, one-minute form — book without the hassle.</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
      {# Decorative pet silhouette / brand illustration #}
      <div class="second-cta__art" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg class="second-cta__art-svg" width="124" height="124" viewBox="0 0 80 80" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true">
          <circle cx="40" cy="52" r="14"/>
          <circle cx="24" cy="34" r="8"/>
          <circle cx="40" cy="24" r="8"/>
          <circle cx="56" cy="34" r="8"/>
          <circle cx="40" cy="40" r="8"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="second-cta__card">
      <form class="hero__form lead-capture-form second-cta__form" method="post" action="/lead" novalidate>
        <input type="hidden" name="city" value="{{ citySlug ?? citySlugAlt ?? '' }}" />
        <input type="hidden" name="service" value="{{ serviceSlug ?? serviceSlugAlt ?? '' }}" />

        <div class="hero__field">
          <label class="hero__label" for="lead2-full-name">Full Name</label>
          <input class="hero__input hero__input--icon hero__input--icon-name" type="text" id="lead2-full-name" name="full_name" placeholder="Your full name" autocomplete="name" required />
        </div>

        <div class="hero__field">
          <label class="hero__label" for="lead2-phone">Phone Number</label>
          <input class="hero__input hero__input--icon hero__input--icon-phone" type="tel" id="lead2-phone" name="phone" placeholder="(555) 123-4567" inputmode="tel" autocomplete="tel" required />
        </div>

        <div class="hero__field">
          <label class="hero__label" for="lead2-email">Email</label>
          <input class="hero__input" type="email" id="lead2-email" name="email" placeholder="you@example.com" autocomplete="email" />
        </div>

        <div class="hero__field">
          <label class="hero__label" for="lead2-pet-type">Pet Type</label>
          <select class="hero__input hero__input--icon hero__input--icon-paw" id="lead2-pet-type" name="pet_type" required>
            <option value="" disabled selected>Select pet type</option>
            <option value="dog">Dog</option>
            <option value="cat">Cat</option>
          </select>
        </div>

        <div class="hero__field">
          <label class="hero__label" for="lead2-breed">Breed / Size</label>
          <input class="hero__input hero__input--icon hero__input--icon-breed" type="text" id="lead2-breed" name="breed_size" placeholder="e.g., Golden Retriever, Large" autocomplete="off" />
        </div>

        {# Honeypot field (hidden) #}
        <div class="visually-hidden" aria-hidden="true" style="position:absolute; left:-10000px;">
          <label for="lead2-website">Website</label>
          <input type="text" id="lead2-website" name="website" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" />
        </div>

        <div class="hero__field">
          <label class="hero__label" for="lead2-consent">
            <input type="checkbox" id="lead2-consent" name="consent_to_share" required />
            I agree to be contacted by relevant groomers via phone or email
          </label>
        </div>

        {# CAPTCHA widget #}
        {% if captcha_provider is defined and captcha_provider|lower != 'none' and captcha_provider|length > 0 %}
          <div class="hero__field captcha-field">
            {% if captcha_provider|lower in ['recaptcha', 'google'] %}
              <div class="g-recaptcha" data-sitekey="{{ recaptcha_site_key|default('') }}"></div>
            {% elseif captcha_provider|lower == 'hcaptcha' %}
              <div class="h-captcha" data-sitekey="{{ hcaptcha_site_key|default('') }}"></div>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        {% endif %}

        <button type="submit" class="hero__cta btn btn--accent" aria-describedby="second-cta-privacy">Get My Free Quote</button>
        <p id="second-cta-privacy" class="second-cta__note">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
            <path d="M6 10V8a6 6 0 1 1 12 0v2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <rect x="5" y="10" width="14" height="10" rx="2" ry="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
          </svg>
          Your info is private and only shared with a matched groomer.
          By submitting, you agree to our
          <a href="{{ path('app_terms') }}">Terms</a>
          and acknowledge our
          <a href="{{ path('app_privacy') }}">Privacy Policy</a>.
          {% if captcha_provider is defined and captcha_provider|lower != 'none' and captcha_provider|length > 0 %}
            {% if captcha_provider|lower in ['recaptcha', 'google'] %}
              This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and the Google
              <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Privacy Policy</a>
              and
              <a href="https://policies.google.com/terms" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Terms of Service</a>
              apply.
            {% elseif captcha_provider|lower == 'hcaptcha' %}
              This site is protected by hCaptcha and its
              <a href="https://www.hcaptcha.com/privacy" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Privacy Policy</a>
              and
              <a href="https://www.hcaptcha.com/terms" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Terms of Service</a>
              apply.
            {% endif %}
          {% endif %}
        </p>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
